{"tid":2211931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共軍東部戰區突po MV「假如戰爭今天爆發」","createTime":"2020-09-21T12:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T01:42:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b95c22116ce9923390d1182053783a4869c1df7","tid":2211931,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_Ob.fnq9jIPL5O15L_dv8Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM1OS44Nzg0MTk0NTI4ODc1Ng--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Aeoy21p73rujW5Uf656dHg--~B/aD0zNzA7dz02NTg7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/43b7f34bf9aa744a6b2e8ca6c4e9d1a5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_Ob.fnq9jIPL5O15L_dv8Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM1OS44Nzg0MTk0NTI4ODc1Ng--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAeoy21p73rujW5Uf656dHg--~B%2FaD0zNzA7dz02NTg7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F43b7f34bf9aa744a6b2e8ca6c4e9d1a5&h=53d35527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解放軍突PO「假如戰爭今天爆發」。（圖／翻攝自東部戰區微博）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院次卿柯拉克（Keith Krach）及日本前首相森喜朗訪台期間，中共連2日派出多架戰機擾台，甚至多次逾越海峽中線，挑釁意味濃厚，導致台海局勢緊繃，微博「東部戰區」突然PO出「假如戰爭今天爆發」的影片，似乎也帶有示警意味。<br />\n<br />\n東部戰區微博今（21）日中午突然PO出宣傳MV，以「假如戰爭今天爆發，這就是我們的回答」為標題，提到「倘若有一天，戰爭打響，我們將背負起祖國的重任和人民的希望，義無反顧，奔向戰場。守護好祖國的一寸一土，一花一草，絕不讓祖國和人民失望！請祖國放心！請人民放心！」<br />\n<br />\n「東部戰區」身為中國解放軍的官方微博，在這個敏感時刻PO出影片，被網友認為警告意味濃厚，其實上周中共才剛在台海實施實戰化演練，當時東部戰區同樣在微博上表示「中國的領土沒有一寸是多餘的，中國一點都不能少，丟掉幻想，準備戰鬥」。<br />\n<br />\n如今又PO出這個影片，中國網友就直言這是「武統前的宣傳工作」，甚至有人表示「前幾天東部戰區在網友武統台灣的評論下面，回復放棄幻想、準備戰鬥，會不會&hellip;」，其他網友也留言「又想去當兵了」、「我孩子也在東部戰區！我支持打」，敏感時刻的PO文格外引發關注。<br />\n<br />\n對於中國的文攻武嚇，總統蔡英文也表示，現在看的不僅是台海的局勢，而是整個區域的整體局勢，她也諷刺「我們一般講的文攻武嚇，這不就是武嚇嗎？我相信這些動作，對中國來講，對他們的國際形象來講沒有幫助！」蔡英文也說，人民能更有警覺，對於中共的本質及存在，對其他國家來講都是有侵略性的，並且帶來威脅，「我們也呼籲中國要自我克制，不要挑釁！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/解放軍突發影片-陸網驚-武統前宣傳-105551449.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87-%E9%99%B8%E7%B6%B2%E9%A9%9A-%E6%AD%A6%E7%B5%B1%E5%89%8D%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3-105551449.html&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZopnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=898d37be\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/解放軍突發影片-陸網驚-武統前宣傳-105551449.html</a>"},{"pid":"d20b7e61bdec32683c7207830440bbc0eae6443d","tid":2211931,"uid":320041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"又唱歌跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8490796c71624583ce3dc0ec762666862d16a5b3","tid":2211931,"uid":11578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"可以拎金像獎了"},{"pid":"7e0688b9ccbd804bfa8097cf39ef4dc5bce759e3","tid":2211931,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"爆撚左啦仲假如<br />\n中印邊境槍都開埋喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d150371f664498fe2239a2a34be45b9099234e","tid":2211931,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"假如戰爭今天爆發<br />\n港 台 回 藏 蒙 整起兵<br />\n加埋 印 美 你點擋"},{"pid":"223f2f2b35886bd3cbbc77f6a50ecf4ff919d27c","tid":2211931,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:26:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=306671273728988&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D306671273728988%26_rdr&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZopnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=b0952680\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=306671273728988&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"f5a9f5cdbc7e6e94adc93bc96a95b48cb9b48806","tid":2211931,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"一半<br />\n<br />\n真係頂唔住要熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a